    "body": "Dedicated files such as spark3XY.RapidsShuffleManager are copied rather than updated during add.shim. \r\n\r\nHowever, it's incorrect to retain the original copyright year (if it's not the same as the current year) . Shimplify.add.shim should replace it. \r\n\r\nSince not all users use pre-commit hooks autocopyright, it could update copyright headers of the remaining files as well.\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @gerashegalov in https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/pull/8020#discussion_r1157611545_\r\n            ",
